]]],", as the glory of the Only Begotten of the Father, full of grace and truth, even the Spirit of truth, which came and dwelt in the flesh, and dwelt among us."]],[12,["And I, John, saw that he received not of the ",["fulness",["study-note-ref","a",[["Philip. 2:8 (6–9)","nt/philip/2.8"],"; ",["Heb. 5:8 (8–9)","nt/heb/5.8"],"."]]]," at the first, but received ",["grace",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 1:16","nt/john/1.16"],"."]]]," for grace;"]],[13,["And he received not of the fulness at first, but continued from ",["grace",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 2:52","nt/luke/2.52"],". ",["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]]," to grace, until he received a fulness;"]],[14,["And thus he was called the ",["Son of God",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 1:16 (1–16)","nt/matt/1.16"],"; ",["Luke 20:41","nt/luke/20.41"],". ",["TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship","tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"],"."]]],", because he received not of the fulness at the first."]],[15,["And I, ",["John",["study-note-ref","a",[["John 1:32 (15–32)","nt/john/1.32"],". ",["TG Holy Ghost, Dove, Sign of","tg/holy-ghost-dove-sign-of"],"."]]],", bear record, and lo, the heavens were opened, and the Holy Ghost descended upon him in the form of a dove, and sat upon him, and there came a voice out of heaven saying: This is my ",["beloved Son",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Witness of the Father","tg/witness-of-the-father"],"."]]],"."]],[16,["And I, John, bear record that he received a fulness of the glory of the Father;"]],[17,["And he received ",["all",["study-note-ref","a",[["Matt. 28:18","nt/matt/28.18"],"; ",["John 17:2","nt/john/17.2"],"; ",["1 Cor. 15:27","nt/1-cor/15.27"],"; ",["Heb. 1:2","nt/heb/1.2"],"; ",["1 Pet. 3:22","nt/1-pet/3.22"],"; ",["D&C 84:28","dc-testament/dc/84.28"],"."]]]," ",["power",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"; ",["God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Authority of","tg/jesus-christ-authority-of"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Power of","tg/jesus-christ-power-of"],"."]]],", both in heaven and on earth, and the glory of the Father was with him, for he dwelt in him."]],[18,["And it shall come to pass, that if you are faithful you shall receive the ",["fulness",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Scriptures to Come Forth","tg/scriptures-to-come-forth"],"."]]]," of the record of John."]],[19,["I give unto you these sayings that you may understand and know how to worship, and ",["know",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 4:8","nt/luke/4.8"],"; ",["John 4:22 (5–26)","nt/john/4.22"],"; ",["Acts 17:23 (22–25)","nt/acts/17.23"],"; ",["Alma 21:22 (21–22)","bofm/alma/21.22"],"; ",["D&C 43:8 (8–9)","dc-testament/dc/43.8"],"; ",["134:4 (1–4)","dc-testament/dc/134.4"],"; ",["A of F 1:11","pgp/a-of-f/1.11"],". ",["TG Discernment, Spiritual","tg/discernment-spiritual"],"; ",["Worship","tg/worship"],"."]]]," what you worship, that you may come unto the Father in my name, and in due time receive of his fulness."]],[20,["For if you keep my ",["commandments",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 8:1 (1–2)","ot/deut/8.1"],"."]]]," you shall receive of his ",["fulness",["study-note-ref","b",[["John 1:16","nt/john/1.16"],"."]]],", and be ",["glorified",["study-note-ref","c",[["John 17:22 (5, 22)","nt/john/17.22"],". ",["TG Man, Potential to Become like Heavenly Father","tg/man-potential-to-become-like-heavenly-father"],"."]]]," in me as I am in the Father; therefore, I say unto you, you shall receive ",["grace",["study-note-ref","d",[["Isa. 28:13 (9–13)","ot/isa/28.13"],". ",["TG Grace","tg/grace"],"."]]]," for grace."]],[21,["And now, verily I say unto you, I was in the ",["beginning",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Foreordained","tg/jesus-christ-foreordained"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Relationships with the Father","tg/jesus-christ-relationships-with-the-father"],"."]]]," with the Father, and am the ",["Firstborn",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship","tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"],"; ",["Jesus Christ, Firstborn","t