l have an inheritance with me—"]],[46,["I called you ",["servants",["study-note-ref","a",[["Lev. 25:55","ot/lev/25.55"],"; ",["1 Ne. 21:3 (3–6)","bofm/1-ne/21.3"],". ",["TG Servant","tg/servant"],"."]]]," for the world’s sake, and ye are their servants for my sake—"]],[47,["And now, verily I say unto Joseph Smith, Jun.—You have not kept the commandments, and must needs stand ",["rebuked",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 95:1 (1–2)","dc-testament/dc/95.1"],". ",["TG Chastening","tg/chastening"],"."]]]," before the Lord;"]],[48,["Your ",["family",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Family, Children, Duties of","tg/family-children-duties-of"],"."]]]," must needs repent and forsake some things, and give more earnest heed unto your sayings, or be removed out of their place."]],[49,["What I say unto one I say unto all; ",["pray",["study-note-ref","a",[["3 Ne. 18:15 (15–21)","bofm/3-ne/18.15"],"."]]]," always lest that wicked one have power in you, and remove you out of your place."]],[50,["My servant Newel K. Whitney also, a bishop of my church, hath need to be ",["chastened",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Reproof","tg/reproof"],"; ",["Warn","tg/warn"],"."]]],", and set in ",["order",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Order","tg/order"],"."]]]," his family, and see that they are more ",["diligent",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Diligence","tg/diligence"],"."]]]," and concerned at home, and pray always, or they shall be removed out of their ",["place",["study-note-ref","d",[["D&C 64:40","dc-testament/dc/64.40"],"."]]],"."]],[51,["Now, I say unto you, my friends, let my servant Sidney Rigdon go on his journey, and make haste, and also proclaim the ",["acceptable",["study-note-ref","a",[["Luke 4:19","nt/luke/4.19"],"; ",["2 Cor. 6:2","nt/2-cor/6.2"],"."]]]," year of the Lord, and the ",["gospel",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 1:13","nt/eph/1.13"],"."]]]," of salvation, as I shall give him utterance; and by your prayer of faith with one consent I will uphold him."]],[52,["And let my servants Joseph Smith, Jun., and Frederick G. Williams make haste also, and it shall be given them even according to the prayer of faith; and inasmuch as you keep my sayings you shall not be confounded in this world, nor in the world to come."]],[53,["And, verily I say unto you, that it is my will that you should ",["hasten",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 45:60 (60–61)","dc-testament/dc/45.60"],"; ",["73:3","dc-testament/dc/73.3"],"; ",["76:15","dc-testament/dc/76.15"],"; ",["91:3","dc-testament/dc/91.3"],"; ",["94:10","dc-testament/dc/94.10"],"."]]]," to ",["translate my scriptures",["study-note-ref","b",["IE the translation of the Bible."]]],", and to ",["obtain",["study-note-ref","c",[["D&C 88:78 (76–80)","dc-testament/dc/88.78"],", ",["118","dc-testament/dc/88.118"],"; ",["90:15","dc-testament/dc/90.15"],"."]]]," a ",["knowledge",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Education","tg/education"],"; ",["Knowledge","tg/knowledge"],"; ",["Learn","tg/learn"],"."]]]," of history, and of countries, and of kingdoms, of ",["laws",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG God, Law of","tg/god-law-of"],"."]]]," of God and man, and all this for the salvation of Zion. Amen."]]],"volume":"dc-testament"}